OL,3,CScotland play Morocco at World Cup
OL,4,C2026 as fans flood Boston
OL,6,FScotland fans have returned to Boston
OL,7,Fahead of their World Cup game against
OL,8,FMorocco on Friday, who present a
OL,9,Fsignificant step up compared to their
OL,10,Fprevious opponents, Haiti.
OL,12,FThe Tartan Army are currently at the
OL,13,Ftop of Group C after beating Haiti in
OL,14,Ftheir opening game 1-0, but they still
OL,15,Fhave to beat two top teams to maintain
OL,16,Ftheir position.
OL,18,FScotland are ranked 37th in the world,
OL,19,Fwhile Morocco are ranked 6th, just
OL,20,Fbehind their Group C rivals Brazil.
OL,21,FHaiti are ranked 85th.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
