PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781939880
OL,3,CScotland play Morocco at World Cup
OL,4,C2026 as fans flood Boston
OL,6,FMorocco and Brazil tied 1-1 in their
OL,7,Fopener.
OL,9,FSpeaking ahead of the game, Scotland
OL,10,Fmanager Steve Clarke said: "Against
OL,11,Fdifficult opponents, we have to be
OL,12,Fvery good. We understand that.
OL,14,F"But sometimes the Scottish psyche and
OL,15,Fthe Scottish mentality means we are a
OL,16,Flittle bit more comfortable when we
OL,17,Fare the underdogs.
OL,19,F"We were the favourites against Haiti
OL,20,Fand we found the game a struggle but
OL,21,Fwe managed to win.
OL,26,@rD@\OUvD@AOU{D@AOU
