OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781939880
OL,3,CScotland play Morocco at World Cup
OL,4,C2026 as fans flood Boston
OL,6,F"This time we are the underdogs and
OL,7,Fsometimes Scotland prefer it that way."
OL,9,FScottish fans' joyous celebrations and
OL,10,Fantics in Boston since they arrived
OL,11,Fahead of their game against Haiti on
OL,12,FJune 14 have attracted significant
OL,13,Fmedia coverage by the US press.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
