PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781939880
OL,3,CScotland play Morocco at World Cup
OL,4,C2026 as fans flood Boston
OL,6,FOne story saw nuns singing "No
OL,7,FScotland, No Party" and another saw
OL,8,Fthe symbolic legalisation of haggis in
OL,9,FMassachusetts by the state's governor,
OL,10,Fwhile Scots have been recapturing the
OL,11,FDuke of Wellington in Glasgow by
OL,12,Fplacing cones on top of statues.
OL,14,FOther outlets reported emergency
OL,15,Flevels of beer being ordered in bars
OL,16,Ffollowing visits from the Tartan Army.
OL,18,FThe mayor of Boston, Michelle Wu, said
OL,19,Fshe joined in the fun and put a cone
OL,20,Fon a statue of Bill Russell.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@SO]
