OL,3,CScotland play Morocco at World Cup
OL,4,C2026 as fans flood Boston
OL,6,FWu said: "No Scotland, no party' has
OL,7,Fbeen absolutely been stuck in my head
OL,8,Fall the time."
OL,10,FShe went on to say: "I think one other
OL,11,Fbit of incredible feedback that I've
OL,12,Fgotten is that in space after space,
OL,13,Fwhere the Tartan Army has has
OL,14,Foccupied, whether it is the fan march
OL,15,For other spaces, they're cleaning up
OL,16,Fafter themselves completely."
OL,26,@rD@UOUxD@]O]
