OL,3,CScotland play Morocco at World Cup
OL,4,C2026 as fans flood Boston
OL,6,FMs Wu added: "They're gathering all
OL,7,Fthe litter, putting it away when the
OL,8,Ftrash cans are overflowed, putting it
OL,9,Fin a little pile next to the trash
OL,10,Fcans.
OL,12,F"It's a mayor's dream, really."
